## ğŸ§ª PART 1 â€“ SQL Analysis

The following analyses were performed using SQL:

1. Total active vs churned customers (by Subscription Type)
2. Average feedback score by Subscription Type and Gender
3. Customers with <5 sessions and feedback <5
4. Customers inactive for more than 60 days
5. Churn rate by Subscription Type
6. Top 10 customers with longest subscriptions
7. Age group-wise churn analysis

